      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IRON LADY (7) ran below best last time finishing seventh (22.78) over 400m at Maitland from Box 2. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. STYLISH EYES (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (23.46) in a Grade 5 at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can figure in the finish. STARLIGHT DUKE (4) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner three back (23.21) at this track over 400m. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Rates a winning chance on best. AUSSIE AUDREY (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
